text: Fuyuko, can I talk to you for a moment?
Here, use this if you’d like.

You’ve been working nonstop lately, right?
It’s a thank you for all your hard work...

I thought it might help you relax a bit
and relieve some of your fatigue.

...What’s that supposed to mean?
Are you saying I don’t always work hard?
No, that’s not what I meant...
